<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Placed - Rivaj</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background: #f5f5f5;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .success-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 50px 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 480px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .success-icon {
            font-size: 60px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .success-card h1 {
            font-size: 26px;
            color: #7a1f54;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .success-card p {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 6px;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: #7a1f54;
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: #611742;
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: #eee;
            color: #333;
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: #ddd;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="success-card">
    <div class="success-icon">🎉</div>
    <h1>Order Placed Successfully!</h1>
    <p>Thank you for your order. Your products will be delivered soon!</p>

    <div>
        <a href="/products" class="btn btn-primary">Continue Shopping</a>
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary">Go Home</a>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>